	</div>	<div id="blog-post-344438688599723618" class="blog-post">
	
	
		<div class="blog-header">
			<h2 class="blog-title">
					<a class="blog-title-link blog-link" href="//mackayenglish.weebly.com/blog/go-against-the-man">go against the man</a>

			</h2>
			<p class="blog-date">
					<span class="date-text">
		5/28/2015
	</span>

			</p>
			<p class="blog-comments">
					<a href="//mackayenglish.weebly.com/blog/go-against-the-man#comments" class="blog-link">
		0 Comments
	</a>

			</p>
		</div>
	
		<div class="blog-separator">&nbsp;</div>
	
		<div class="blog-content">
				<div class="paragraph" style="text-align:justify;"><font size="3"><strong><span "font-family:arial;="" mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;times="" roman&quot;;color:black"=""><span id="selectionBoundary_1432870367504_8444863317999989" class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="display: none;">&#65279;</span>Power and corruption in animal farm starts small, seemingly mindless or even logical things, such as the pigs keeping the milk and apples for themselves. But, soon the pigs obtain absolute power and therefore <a href="http://www.shmoop.com/animal-farm/power-leadership-corruption-theme.html" title="">absolute corruption</a>. Along the way, the other animal&rsquo;s concerns and/or even slightly rebellious notions are quickly simmered and persuaded away by the pig&rsquo;s smooth logic and words. </span><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span>  <span "font-family:arial;="" mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;times="" roman&quot;;color:black"="">In today&rsquo;s society, that&rsquo;s not how things work. People are not so easily shushed. People stand up for what they believe is right whether is be peaceful protest, violent riots, awareness groups, making something that goes viral, art, stand-up comedy, music, and so much more. People stand up against the government, stand up for their equal rights, and oppose customs and ideas for valid reasons and even just for the sake of opposing.</span><span "font-size:10.0pt;font-family:times;="" mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;times="" roman&quot;"="" style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span>  <span "font-family:arial;="" color:black"="">In no way am I trying to say that people are not easily persuaded. Conformity and propaganda are prominent issue and the human race is reasonably gullible. However, there will always be people who will try to right things when they&rsquo;ve been wronged. No matter the consequences or restrictions people will rebel and stand up for themselves. </span><br /><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span>  <span "font-family:arial;="" color:black"="">In Animal Farm, this idea of rebelling against the rebellion never crosses any of the animal&rsquo;s minds. When the pigs are suppressing the other animals and when the pigs begin to break their own set rules none of the other animals have the guts or maybe just not the brains to stand up for what&rsquo;s right.</span><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span>  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></font><span style=""><font size="3"><strong>Intellectual rebellion is more effective, not just f!#% The man stuff, but real facts and a strong argument or powerful way of presentation. The best examples of these are:</strong></font><span id="selectionBoundary_1432870367504_7031054948456585" class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">&#65279;</span></span><br /><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span>  <span style=""><font size="4">Speaking out through art (Banksy)</font></span><br /><span style=""></span></div>  <div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:center"> <a href='https://www.popularresistance.org/bloomberg-threatens-bansky-with-arrest-for-outside-art/'> <img src="/uploads/5/0/9/4/50940509/4634351_orig.jpeg" alt="Picture" style="width:auto;max-width:100%" /> </a> <div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div> </div></div>  <div class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;"><span style="">It's beautiful, the art, the statement, Banksy is known for his power to cause viewers to think</span><br /><span style=""><br /></span><br /><span style=""><font size="4">Satirical stand up comedians</font></span><br /><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span></div>  <div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:left"> <a href='https://www.pinterest.com/explore/comedy-quotes/'> <img src="/uploads/5/0/9/4/50940509/2715984_orig.jpg" alt="Picture" style="width:auto;max-width:100%" /> </a> <div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div> </div></div>  <div class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">-Hilarious, Clever, Relatable all perfect factors to make his point stick in your mind and stick out in your mind<br /><br /><font size="4">Rap and/or hip-hop <a href="http://www.hiphoparea.com/rap/hip-hops-ideologies-of-rebellion.html" title="">examples</a></font><br /><br /><br /><font size="4"><em><u>"Cops is anxious to put niggaz in handcuffs&nbsp;<br />They wanna hang us, see us dead, enslave us&nbsp;<br />Keep us trapped in the same place we raised in&nbsp;<br />Then they wonder why we act so outrageous&nbsp;<br />Run around stressed out and pull out gauges&nbsp;<br />Cause every time you let the animal out cages&nbsp;<br />It's dangerous, to people who look like strangers&nbsp;"<br /><span style=""></span><br />~"The Watcher" by Dr. Dre</u></em></font><br /><br /><span style=""><strong><font size="3">People use these methods to express themselves and their ideas. However, they not only use it for expression but for awareness and even to promote people to rally against or for certain ideas. Art uses class and cleverness to express these ideas making it more effective. Comedians use humor and cleverness to make their opinions and points effective and memorable. Rap and hip hop use rhyme, pop culture, and once again, of course, cleverness. All of these things have a common variable, wit. So, maybe the animals didn&rsquo;t have the smarts to see there was a problem with their society, or perhaps they just didn&rsquo;t have the wit to express it in a meaningful or convincing way.</font></strong></span><br /><br /><font size="4">Want more?<br />Of course you do.</font><br /><span style=""></span><br /><span style=""></span></div>  <div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:left"> <a> <img src="/uploads/5/0/9/4/50940509/297547.jpg?1432869091" alt="Picture" style="width:auto;max-width:100%" /> </a> <div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div> </div></div>  <div class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;"><u><font size="4"><em>"Something provoked the whole globe to lower expectations&nbsp;<br />Damn, what's wrong with my generation?&nbsp;<br />We was the cream of the crop but it seems we've been robbed&nbsp;<br />That's what happens when you trade in all your dreams for a job&nbsp;<br />And every day it gets less and less exciting&nbsp;<br />I would make a difference but I'm busy faking this instead of trying</em>&nbsp;"<br /><br />~"Exhausted Love"by Eyedea and Abilities</font></u></div>  <div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:center"> <a href='http://www.engadget.com/2014/04/14/banksys-latest-works-tackle-technology/'> <img src="/uploads/5/0/9/4/50940509/4556269_orig.jpeg" alt="Picture" style="width:auto;max-width:100%" /> </a> <div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div> </div></div>  <div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:left"> <a href='https://televisionwithtommy.wordpress.com/2014/03/07/comedians-stand-up-comedy-and-netflix/'> <img src="/uploads/5/0/9/4/50940509/8967622.jpg?1432869561" alt="Picture" style="width:auto;max-width:100%" /> </a> <div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div> </div></div>  <div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:center"> <a href='https://flipboard.com/topic/northamerica'> <img src="/uploads/5/0/9/4/50940509/5062432_orig.jpg" alt="Picture" style="width:auto;max-width:100%" /> </a> <div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div> </div></div>  <div class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;"><font size="4"><u><em>"Like the C.I.A. be bringin' in crack cocaine bailin' out of planes&nbsp;<br />With the George Bush connections, I push reflection&nbsp;<br />Like I'm sellin' izm, like a dealer buildin' the system&nbsp;<br />Supply and the demand it's all capitalism</em>&nbsp;"<br /><br /></u></font><br /><font size="4"><u>~"Manifesto" by Talib Kweli</u></font><br /></div>

